About Us





Established in 1867, Babcock & Wilcox is a global leader in advanced energy and environmental technologies and services for the power and industrial markets, with operations, subsidiaries and joint ventures worldwide.
B&W’s Global Power, Global Services and Industrial Environmental segments align with our three-pronged strategy to drive EPS growth and shareholder value.
    Optimize traditional business to align with changing markets
Pursue growth opportunities in international markets
Continue disciplined acquisition program

