en $2.08 and $2.62, with an estimated average price of $2.3. The stock is now traded at around $2.99. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.75%. The holdings were 916,791 shares as of 2017-03-31.Added: Black Diamond Inc (BDE)Wynnefield Capital Inc added to the holdings in Black Diamond Inc by 23.88%. The purchase prices were between $5.25 and $6, with an estimated average price of $5.62. The stock is now traded at around $6.00. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.53%. The holdings were 1,444,022 shares as of 2017-03-31.Added: Neptune Technologies & Bioressources Inc (NEPT)Wynnefield Capital Inc added to the holdings in Neptune Technologies & Bioressources Inc by 82.55%. The purchase prices were between $0.97 and $1.16, with an estimated average price of $1.05. The stock is now traded at around $1.00. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.29%. The holdings were 1,825,450 shares as of 2017-03-31.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 2 Warning Signs with BDE. Click here to check it out.BDE 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of BDEPeter Lynch Chart of BDEPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



