Transforming our World for 150 Years 



									Explore B&W's Legacy
								





























WHAT WE DO
Headquartered in North Carolina, USA, B&W is a global leader in energy and environmental technologies and services for power, renewable and industrial markets. B&W companies employ nearly 6,000 people around the world.

























 





Power








Energy and Environmental
We're committed to reliable, efficient and environmentally sustainable fossil fuel power. B&W customers around the world depend on us for proven turnkey systems, custom-designed technologies, retrofits, parts, services and more.

Power Segment 






 





Renewable








Building a Circular Economy
Waste-to-energy and biomass fuels are an ecologically sound, cost-effective means of energy recovery to produce electricity and/or heat. With more than 80 years of experience in renewable energy, B&W technologies and turnkey solutions provide measurable results and boundless benefits.

Renewable Segment 






 





Industrial








Serving Diverse, Global End Markets
With custom-engineered technologies for pollution control, coating, drying, li-ion electrode coating, process steam generation, cooling, heat recovery and other applications - B&W serves a wide range of industrial customers worldwide.

Industrial Segment 




























